#### Tips:

* You can use the , and . keys to move forward or backward through different images in the folder you’re in  
* If you would like the preset to load in in a different location each time: load it in, adjust, then click save preset  
* If you’re confident in the bounding boxes of the leads, you can run an entire folder at once. Under Folder, open your desired folder. Then load Preset 1, adjust the bounding box to what you want for all files in the folder. Then under Folder, click Process Folder. This process could take a while.
